name: Catch the Fly Cat Game
description:
A very simple little cat entertainment game; see how many times your CAT can catch the flying insect. A counter will keep track of your cat's scores.

You can choose between 3 flying insects (fly, mosquito or moth) and 6 different backgrounds.

A "warning"; iPad games are not for all cats. I can't guarantee that your cat will like this game or play it at all. Cats are different - just like us : ) But MY cats love it!
